WEBVTT

00:03:59.801 --> 00:04:01.604
How could I help these people?

00:04:01.628 --> 00:04:04.666
I am one individual.
What can I do for them?

00:04:05.205 --> 00:04:07.848
But at that moment, I knew

00:04:07.872 --> 00:04:10.419
that education changed my life.

00:04:10.745 --> 00:04:14.459
It transformed me. It gave me status.

00:04:14.483 --> 00:04:18.114
It gave me confidence.
It gave me a career.

00:04:18.138 --> 00:04:20.352
It helped me to support my family,

00:04:20.376 --> 00:04:22.831
to bring my family to another country,

00:04:22.855 --> 00:04:24.019
to be safe.

00:04:24.853 --> 00:04:27.590
And I knew that at that moment

00:04:27.614 --> 00:04:31.622
that what I should give to my people
is education and health,